	(text "All vehicle connectors are screw terminal suitable for 2.5mm cable.  GND is common on all ports.\nThe case will have silicon seal where the cablkes enter.  The case top is removable.\nThe 6 wire connection between this expansion box and the gauge will be on a pluggagble connector \nat each end for easy removal of the dash.  I'll provide the made up cable for that.\nThere are spar inputs and outputs available.  They could be used for control of interior lights\nand the steps for example turning off the interior lights and folding the steps a few seconds\nafter the door closes.  I'll layout the relay box for the fan control to replace the rats nest \nI had previously"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 67.564 178.562 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "c8cf0193-24ce-4993-a884-054fde3b1a87")
	)
